Subject: [PATCH] netfilter: nf_tables: clone set on flush only
References: bsc#1258210
Patch-mainline: 6.18.17
Git-commit: fb7fb4016300ac622c964069e286dc83166a5d52

[ Upstream commit fb7fb4016300ac622c964069e286dc83166a5d52 ]

